items.title: Awesome Hacking
items.content_text:
### Tools / Other

*   [CSP Scanner](https://cspscanner.com/) - Analyze a site's Content-Security-Policy (CSP) to find bypasses and missing directives.
*   [RustScan (‚≠ê17k)](https://github.com/rustscan/rustscan) - Extremely fast port scanner built with Rust, designed to scan all ports in a couple of seconds and utilizes nmap to perform port enumeration in a fraction of the time.
